I'm fine.

48
00:03:26,550 --> 00:03:28,500
She's my girlfriend, Shuangshuang.

49
00:03:28,500 --> 00:03:29,340
Mike.

50
00:03:30,500 --> 00:03:31,730
We came for the match.

51
00:03:31,730 --> 00:03:34,730
Let's see how it turns out.

52
00:03:40,460 --> 00:03:41,330
Antonio,

53
00:03:41,380 --> 00:03:42,460
