54
00:03:42,460 --> 00:03:43,370
Wait for me.

55
00:03:43,370 --> 00:03:44,440
Sure, no problem.

56
00:03:44,440 --> 00:03:45,320
Sorry.

57
00:03:45,320 --> 00:03:46,300
