72
00:04:22,870 --> 00:04:23,760
Make up an excuse.

73
00:04:23,760 --> 00:04:25,640
Tell him you're not feeling well
or whatever.

74
00:04:25,640 --> 00:04:26,480
You're good at that.

75
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:27,320
- Right?
- No.

76
00:04:27,320 --> 00:04:28,060
Antonio is

77
00:04:28,060 --> 00:04:29,160
a lifetime VIP member here.

78
00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:30,010
I can't be

79
00:04:30,010 --> 00:04:31,100
"not feeling well" forever.

80
00:04:32,930 --> 00:04:33,910
Have you thought

81
00:04:33,910 --> 00:04:35,110
about being honest with him?

82
00:04:35,110 --> 00:04:36,380
Like telling him about your past.

83
00:04:36,380 --> 00:04:38,080
