to teach me how to date.

84
00:04:40,170 --> 00:04:41,100
I'm not your client.

85
00:04:41,100 --> 00:04:42,370
Why do you care so much about me?

86
00:04:47,710 --> 00:04:48,620
Fine, I'm leaving.

87
00:04:49,350 --> 00:04:50,840
I'd suggest you not watch the fight.

88
00:04:56,780 --> 00:04:58,180
It really matches your eyes.

89
00:04:58,180 --> 00:04:59,350
Thank you.

90
00:05:01,180 --> 00:05:02,170
Wait just a moment.

91
00:05:03,900 --> 00:05:05,400
- Hello.
- Hello.

92
00:05:05,890 --> 00:05:06,730
Come here.

93
00:05:07,780 --> 00:05:08,620
Me too.

94
00:05:08,790 --> 00:05:10,180
Let me introduce you.

95
00:05:10,180 --> 00:05:11,930
This is Mr. He from Highland.

96
00:05:12,220 --> 00:05:13,820
This is Shuangshuang, my girlfriend.

97
00:05:13,820 --> 00:05:14,940
I've heard so much about you.

98
00:05:14,940 --> 00:05:15,820
Pleasure to meet you.

99
00:05:15,820 --> 00:05:16,760
This is Mike.

100
00:05:23,460 --> 00:05:25,110
The show is about to begin.

101
00:05:25,660 --> 00:05:27,280
Everyone, inside, please.

102
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:33,880
Hi.

103
00:05:50,440 --> 00:05:51,380
And now,

104
00:05:51,380 --> 00:05:54,410
