105
00:05:54,520 --> 00:05:55,690
Coming to the stage...

106
00:05:55,810 --> 00:05:58,190
- Big Beast.
- It's about to start.

107
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,560
Go, Big Beast!

108
00:06:05,580 --> 00:06:07,300
Come on, Big Beast!

109
00:06:15,270 --> 00:06:16,400
Fighting

110
