112
00:06:29,580 --> 00:06:30,740
(Liu Yan)

113
00:06:32,460 --> 00:06:35,100
Big Beast, go!

114
00:06:36,060 --> 00:06:37,380
Isn't she from Xiya?

115
00:06:38,900 --> 00:06:40,380
You knew her before?

116
00:06:42,660 --> 00:06:44,180
She visited my mother's grave.

117
00:06:45,260 --> 00:06:46,780
Something must have happened.

118
00:06:46,780 --> 00:06:48,460
Otherwise, she wouldn't have come here.

119
00:07:00,940 --> 00:07:03,260
(Production: Roses)
Scene 1, shot 1, take 1. Action!

120
00:07:06,220 --> 00:07:08,780
Ladies and gentlemen,

121
00:07:08,780 --> 00:07:10,740
get ready to watch another

122
00:07:10,740 --> 00:07:12,940
two warriors facing off in the ring.

123
00:07:12,940 --> 00:07:14,540
There ain't no scoring.

124
00:07:14,540 --> 00:07:16,280
No time limit.

125
00:07:16,280 --> 00:07:18,540
No holds barred match.

126
00:07:18,540 --> 00:07:21,290
Get ready for combat!

127
00:07:21,290 --> 00:07:22,520
Ready? Beat!

128
00:07:53,370 --> 00:07:54,580
Get up.

129
00:07:54,580 --> 00:07:55,640
Where's the referee?

130
00:09:05,980 --> 00:09:07,500
It has to stop. Can't you see?

131
00:09:12,020 --> 00:09:13,060
Go back to your seat.

132
00:09:31,160 --> 00:09:32,450
So, you've made up your mind?

133
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:33,800
I have.

134
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:42,340
You're going to die,

135
00:09:42,340 --> 00:09:43,180
right?

136
00:09:44,390 --> 00:09:45,290
Maybe.

137
00:09:46,980 --> 00:09:48,880
Maybe it's better
to rip the bandage off.

138
00:09:50,020 --> 00:09:51,690
I've been running for too long.

139
00:09:52,760 --> 00:09:54,760
I ran from debt collectors
with my mom as a kid.

140
00:09:55,580 --> 00:09:56,960
Now I'm running with Li Zan.

141
00:09:58,660 --> 00:09:59,620
I'm tired.

142
00:10:02,260 --> 00:10:03,980
The best thing Jiang Fang ever did

143
00:10:04,740 --> 00:10:06,180
was send me to sports school.

144
00:10:06,740 --> 00:10:07,960
That's where I learned

145
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:09,270
how to face my fears.

146
00:10:11,020 --> 00:10:12,130
I used to hope

147
00:10:12,130 --> 00:10:13,660
that by the time she came back for me,

148
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:15,260
I'd have already won

149
00:10:15,260 --> 00:10:16,440
enough matches,

150
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:17,830
so she'd never have to run again.

151
00:10:19,950 --> 00:10:21,420
I wanted to tell her in person.

152
00:10:22,380 --> 00:10:23,460
Jiang Fang,

153
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:25,660
I can protect you now.

154
00:10:26,120 --> 00:10:27,380
Don't hide anymore.

155
00:10:28,420 --> 00:10:30,680
Can you be brave for me just once?

156
00:10:30,970 --> 00:10:32,090
Come and find me.

157
00:10:33,180 --> 00:10:34,940
Even if I die,

158
00:10:35,700 --> 00:10:37,770
I want you to remember
you had a Salty

159
00:10:37,770 --> 00:10:39,500
