634
00:43:39,420 --> 00:43:40,340
Surprise.

635
00:43:44,230 --> 00:43:45,090
Listen.

636
00:43:45,420 --> 00:43:46,850
You can see everything you can see

637
00:43:46,850 --> 00:43:48,100
on the Ferris wheel from here.

638
00:43:52,650 --> 00:43:54,400
How is it? Cool or what?

639
00:43:55,980 --> 00:43:58,600
♪Is filled with everything I love♪

640
00:43:59,700 --> 00:44:01,120
Look at these lights

641
00:44:01,120 --> 00:44:02,170
I designed.

642
00:44:03,620 --> 00:44:05,420
Compliment me. Come on.

643
00:44:05,680 --> 00:44:06,560
